---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Discover Ugo ROSERAT's journey, a passionate web developer based in Le Mans, from graphic arts to code."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="label">About</span>
      <h1 class="page-title">
        From graphic arts<br />to code<span class="accent">.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="page-intro">
        I'm Ugo ROSERAT, a 23-year-old web developer based in Le Mans, France.
        My atypical background combines artistic training and software development,
        giving me a unique perspective on web projects.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="main-content">
          <div class="content-block">
            <h2>My Journey</h2>
            <p>
              I started with an artistic background, earning a <strong>Vocational
              Certificate in Graphic Signage and Decor</strong> (2018-2020) followed
              by a <strong>Diploma in Arts and Crafts</strong> specializing in graphic
              art and signage (2020-2022). This creative foundation gave me a particular
              sensitivity for design and user experience.
            </p>
            <p>
              In 2022, I began my transition to web development by joining
              <strong>ekod</strong> through a work-study program at ACR Fers Aluminium.
              I earned my Associate Degree in Web Development in 2024 and my Bachelor's
              in Application Design in 2025.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="content-block">
            <h2>Today</h2>
            <p>
              Since August 2025, I've been working full-time at <strong>ACR Fers
              Aluminium</strong> in Ruaudin as Production, Communication, and Software
              Development Manager. I combine my technical skills and creativity to
              develop web solutions tailored to the company's needs.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="content-block">
            <h2>Personal Projects</h2>
            <p>
              In January 2025, I co-founded <strong>Collectif Pixel</strong>, an
              association dedicated to tech and digital culture. With Kevin ALVES,
              a friend I met at ekod, we host the <strong>Pixel Podcast</strong>
              where we discuss development, tech, and our experiences in the field.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="content-block">
            <h2>Achievements</h2>
            <p>
              In 2025, I won the <strong>24h of Code</strong> with a student team
              on the challenge presented by "Le Mans School of AI". I also participated
              in Startup Weekend Le Mans in 2024 and returned as a mentor in 2025.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <aside class="sidebar">
          <div class="info-card">
            <h3>Information</h3>
            <dl>
              <dt>Location</dt>
              <dd>Le Mans, France</dd>
              <dt>Experience</dt>
              <dd>3+ years</dd>
              <dt>Specialty</dt>
              <dd>Web Development</dd>
              <dt>Status</dt>
              <dd>Full-time - ACR Fers Aluminium</dd>
            </dl>
          </div>

          <div class="info-card">
            <h3>Contact</h3>
            <a href="mailto:roserat.ugo@gmail.com" class="contact-link">
                roserat.ugo@gmail.com
            </a>
            <div class="social-links">
              <a href="https://github.com/roseratugo" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
              <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ugo-roserat/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background-color: var(--color-ink);
    color: #ffffff;
    padding: 8rem 1.5rem 5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .page-hero {
      padding: 10rem 3rem 6rem;
    }
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .accent {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      gap: 5rem;
    }
  }

  .main-content {
    max-width: 650px;
  }

  .content-block {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .content-block h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .content-block p {
    color: var(--color-ink-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .content-block strong {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .sidebar {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .info-card {
    background-color: var(--color-paper-warm);
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .info-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .info-card dl {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .info-card dt {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
  }

  .info-card dd {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .contact-link {
    display: block;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .contact-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .social-links a {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-ink-light);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .social-links a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
</style>
